erywhere, touch everything... You never know what you might find. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840110/extras/8911995f8fbf40241e52f137e5c2664c.poster.avif?t=1746807170\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840110/extras/8911995f8fbf40241e52f137e5c2664c.webm?t=1746807170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840110/extras/8911995f8fbf40241e52f137e5c2664c.mp4?t=1746807170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Creatures </strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This house might seem completely empty... But you are certainly not alone. Currently, you must outsmart two creatures, with many more to come in the future. Don't turn your back unless you're sure you're alone.. and don't let Her see you move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840110/extras/f7001e8f67e1e1a08a3ee7053a62e8f4.poster.avif?t=1746807170\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840110/extras/f7001e8f67e1e1a08a3ee7053a62e8f4.webm?t=1746807170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840110/extras/f7001e8f67e1e1a08a3ee7053a62e8f4.mp4?t=1746807170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Limited Visibility</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Did someone turn off the lights? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your trusty flashlight to look around, and navigate through the dollhouse. Don't lose your flashlight, or you might stumble into something you'll have trouble escaping... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840110/extras/4c8ddedcc57720bd26e8a6eb24924c01.poster.avif?t=1746807170\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840110/extras/4c8ddedcc57720bd26e8a6eb24924c01.webm?t=1746807170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840110/extras/4c8ddedcc57720bd26e8a6eb24924c01.mp4?t=1746807170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> VR and non-VR  </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brave the dollhouse in non-VR using the standard mouse and keyboard, Or, if you're feeling fearless, get the full experience and face this nightmare in Virtual Reality. A dollhouse has never felt so real... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840110/extras/94963b62b0e8d0d254ecec39aac12007.poster.avif?t=1746807170\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840110/extras/94963b62b0e8d0d254ecec39aac12007.webm?t=1746807170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840110/extras/94963b62b0e8d0d254ecec39aac12007.mp4?t=1746807170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To content creators and streamers: Please feel free to stream footage of, or otherwise create content using our game! All music and audio content contained within is safe to use on stream.</p>",
